section.p:
You need to setup a database instance. To quickly start up, you may enter mysql and perform the following sequence of statements:
mysql mysql grant all on scarab.* to sa;
In the above sequence we assume, that you will name your database "scarab" and the scarab user will be "sa". There is no password assigned to the user sa. Note: This setup is highly unsecure and only ment to be used for test cases.
